examples.en: Pine trees stood straight along the path.
Sit up straight and don't slouch.
She told him straight to his face that she hated him.
examples.ru: Она сказала ему прямо в лицо, что ненавидит его.

examples.en: She walked straight up to him and slapped him in the face.
examples.ru: Она подошла прямо к нему и дала ему пощёчину.
